n></div></div></header><main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-8 sm:py-10"><div class="mb-8"><h1 class="text-[26px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight">Good afternoon, Richard.</h1><p class="text-[13px] text-slate-500 mt-1.5">Tuesday, May 12, 2026</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-6 sm:mb-8"><a class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-3 sm:p-5 hover:border-slate-400 transition-colors" href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard#pipeline"><div class="text-[22px] sm:text-[28px] font-bold leading-none text-slate-900">15</div><div class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1.5 tracking-[0.07em] uppercase">Companies</div></a><a class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-3 sm:p-5 hover:border-slate-400 transition-colors" href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard#pipeline"><div class="text-[22px] sm:text-[28px] font-bold leading-none text-amber-600">3</div><div class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1.5 tracking-[0.07em] uppercase">Active</div></a><a class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-3 sm:p-5 hover:border-slate-400 transition-colors" href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard/signals"><div class="text-[22px] sm:text-[28px] font-bold leading-none text-amber-600">6</div><div class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1.5 tracking-[0.07em] uppercase">Signals</div></a><a class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-3 sm:p-5 hover:border-slate-400 transition-colors" href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard/calendar"><div class="text-[22px] sm:text-[28px] font-bold leading-none text-red-700">5</div><div class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1.5 tracking-[0.07em] uppercase">Actions Due</div></a></div><a class="mb-6 sm:mb-8 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-5 flex items-center gap-5 hover:border-slate-400 transition-colors block" href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard/contacts"><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-900">1 of 15 companies have a contact</p><p class="text-[12px] text-slate-400 mt-0.5">Roles at this level fill through relationships. Add contacts at your top targets.</p></div><span class="text-[12px] font-semibold text-slate-500 shrink-0">Add contacts →</span></a><div class="mb-6 sm:mb-8"><p class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-slate-400 mb-3">What needs attention</p><div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3"><a class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-4 hover:border-slate-400 transition-colors block" href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard/contacts/new"><div class="text-[26px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none mb-1">14</div><div class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-1.5">companies with no contact</div><div class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">Databricks, Stripe +12 more</div><span class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-500">Add contacts →</span></a><a class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-4 hover:border-slate-400 transition-colors block" href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard/contacts"><div class="text-[26px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none mb-1">2</div><div class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-1.5">contacts not yet reached</div><div class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">People you know but have not yet connected with in this search.</div><span class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-500">Draft outreach →</span></a><a class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-4 hover:border-slate-400 transition-colors block" href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard/companies"><div class="text-[26px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none mb-1">12</div><div class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-1.5">companies with no prep brief</div><div class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">Databricks, Andale +10 more</div><span class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate-500">Run prep briefs →</span></a></div></div><div class="mb-6 sm:mb-8"><div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3"><p class="text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.08em] uppercase text-slate-500">Opportunity Radar</p><p class="text-[11px] text-slate-400">Companies to consider adding</p></div><div class="space-y-2"><div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 p-3.5 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors"><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1 flex-wrap"><span class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-800">OpenAI</span><span class="text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.06em] uppercase text-cyan-700 bg-cyan-50 border border-cyan-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">Expansion</span></div><p class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">OpenAI is rapidly expanding its San Francisco headquarters and enterprise infrastructure teams following their $80B+ valuation and Series C funding, requiring senior IT leadership to scale operations.</p></div><a href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard/companies/new?name=OpenAI" class="text-[12px] font-semibold text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 whitespace-nowrap flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 transition-colors">+ Add</a></div><div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 p-3.5 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors"><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1 flex-wrap"><span class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-800">Databricks</span><span class="text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.06em] uppercase text-cyan-700 bg-cyan-50 border border-cyan-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">Funding</span></div><p class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Databricks recently raised $500M+ at a $43B+ valuation and is headquartered in San Francisco with aggressive growth in enterprise deployments, necessitating IT infrastructure and security leadership.</p></div><a href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard/companies/new?name=Databricks" class="text-[12px] font-semibold text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 whitespace-nowrap flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 transition-colors">+ Add</a></div><div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 p-3.5 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors"><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1 flex-wrap"><span class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-800">Figma</span><span class="text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.06em] uppercase text-cyan-700 bg-cyan-50 border border-cyan-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">Transformation</span></div><p class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">Figma's recent IPO preparation and San Francisco Bay Area headquarters expansion requires modernization of IT systems and network infrastructure to support 1000+ employee growth.</p></div><a href="https://startingmonday.app/dashboard/companies/new?name=Figma" class="text-[12px] font-semibold text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 whitespace-nowrap flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 transition-colors">+ Add</a></div></div></div><div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-5 mb-6 sm:mb-8 flex items-center gap-5"><div class="text-[40px] font-bold leading-none tabular-nums shrink-0 text-slate-300">0</div><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><div class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-slate-900">2 outreach drafts left to hit your goal.</div><div class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 mt-0.5">Goal: 2 per week · 0 done since Monday</div></div><form action="javascript:throw new Error(&#39;A React form was unexpectedly submitted. If you called form.submit() manually, consider using form.requestSubmit() instead. If you\&#39;re trying to use event.stopPropagation() in a submit event handler, consider also calling event.preventDefault().&#39;)" class="shrink-0"><input type="hidden" value="3" name="weekly_goal"><button type="submit" class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 border border-slate-200 rounded px-2.5 py-1 cursor-pointer bg-transparent transition-colors">Goal: 2↑</button></form></div><div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded px-5 py-4 mb-6 sm:mb-8"><p class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-slate-400 mb-3">What works at this level</p><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4"><div><p class="text-[20px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none">12-18</p><p class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 mt-1">target companies in a 90-day search</p></div><div><p class="text-[20px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none">2-3</p><p class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 mt-1">new conversations per week to maintain momentum</p></div><div><p class="text-[20px] font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none">72 hrs</p><p class="text-[12px] text-slate-500 mt-1">typical response time after a warm intro</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded p-5 mb-6 sm:mb-8"><p class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-slate-400 mb-4">Weekly Search Activity</p><div class="recharts-responsive-container" style="width: 100%; height: 150px; min-width: 0px;"><div style="width: 0px; overflow-x: visible;"><div width="806" height="150" class="recharts-wrapper" style="position: relative; cursor: default; width: 806px; height: 150px;"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" tabindex="-1" class="recharts-tooltip-wrapper" style="visibility: hidden; pointer-events: none; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px;"><div class="recharts-default-tooltip" role="status" aria-live="assertive" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(226, 232, 240); white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11px; border-radius: 4px;"><p class="recharts-tooltip-label" style="margin: 0px;"></p></div></div><svg role="application" tabindex="0" class="recharts-surface" width="806" height="150" viewBox="0 0 806 150" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block;"><title></title><desc></desc><g tabindex="-1" class="recharts-zIndex-layer_-100"></g><g tabindex="-1" class="recharts-zIndex-layer_-50"></g><